{
  "stem": "1338.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yep.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one of the things that I forgot to mention, of course, is that I read a lot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And today, when I look back, since I missed two years of high school-- and actually, in the city of Chicago, somebody was questioning my getting an apartment on the South Side when I was working there, because I didn't have a high school degree.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it worked out OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was at the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyway, speaking about the high school, since I didn't finish it, I look back sometimes and I had a wonderful school with wonderful teachers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I really think that most of my education and most of my [INAUDIBLE] but certainly my-- my process of learning and acquiring knowledge and understanding was really, probably, through this reading period.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Libraries were available.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That is, some basements, some places, were always books.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I borrowed them and I read voraciously.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's probably one of the finest periods, as far as self-education goes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I believe it to this very day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As far as humor and life is concerned, there were a lot of humor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sick humor.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some of it, I hate to repeat it here, and I probably could be charged with-- with probably vulgarity and obscenity if I repeated some of the jokes that were going around the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were obscene.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they were humorous, because they were making fun of a situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so there was humor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was life.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I played bridge with my classmates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I have-- there were all kinds of things were going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- not always the same way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "After '42, in September, there was a critical time when children were disappearing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That changed the nature of the place, became more like a camp in that sense.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
